## **Description**
The **DataQuality **operator allows to perform quality checks on input data for the Document Legal Archive profile, based on the configuration settings.

> Important

The **DataQuality **operator can only be used in combination with the Data Quality resource. For more information, see: [DT3 Data Quality](/doxee-platform/docs/dt3-data-quality-component).

## **Input**
**Input**

**Data type**

**Description**

**workunit**

Any

Input file containing information on the work unit

**document**

Any

Input file containing information on the document

**check**

Any

The input data on which to perform the quality check

## **Output**
**Output**

**Data type**

**Description**

**out0**

Boolean

Result of the quality check on input data

## **Settings**
**![](data:image/jpeg;base64,)**

- From the **Profile **drop-down menu, select the required profile.

- From the **Data Quality Check **drop-down menu, select the type of check that you want to perform on input data.

> Note

The different types of checks represent the names of the fields of the DataQuality index file contained in the input package, which can only be read by the Quality component.

- Click **Apply **to confirm.

## **Special cases**
None.
